GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 2nd September, 2001
11 Bhadrapada, 1923 (S)
The undersigned is directed to say that Shri Ashok Pradhan has been
sworn in as Minister of State by the President at 1800 hours, today, the 2nd
September, 2001, in the Rashtrapati Bhawan, New Delhi.
(P. Gopalakrishnan)
